SUMMARY:High Tea Dim Sum at #3 Top Toronto Chinese Restaurant
DESCRIPTION:Experience Toronto\n**On Friday\, April 3rd\, join us for High
  Tea at Lai Wah Heen Restaurant for the launch of their high tea and also 
 recently renovated restaurant.** Enjoy signature dim sum platters\, sweet 
 lotus swan pastries\, specialty teas\, and discounted cocktails and bites 
 all afternoon! Since reopening last year\, the response from the city has 
 been incredible\, with recognition from **[Toronto Life](http://links.rmc.
