SUMMARY:The Sea Star Ball with Dance Lesson\, Cocktails+++ at Ripley's Aqu
 arium
DESCRIPTION:Experience Toronto\nOn **Friday\, April 17th**\, attend the **
 Sea Star Ball when Ripley's Aquarium will host its Regency-inspired Spring
  Ball\, an affair where elegance reigns and the ocean provides a most ench
 anting backdrop**. For one glittering night of revelry and romance\, the A
 quarium's galleries will be transformed into a setting worthy of the Ton. 
 Guests are encouraged to don their finest attire as they promenade through
  shimmering aquatic exhibits\, take dance lessons among the stingrays and 
 sip on custom cocktails at their tropical reefs. **Purchase Sea Star Ball 
 on Friday April 17th at 8pm.**\n\n**What's Included:**\n\n* Free Photo-ops
 \n* Surprise Giveaways\n* Whisky Lounge\n* Group Dance Lessons – Waltz\n
 * PLUS - Present yourself to the Queen of the Seven Seas!\n\n**COST**\nAdu
 lt: $62.50 + taxes\n\nMeetup Organizer Fee: $5\n\n**Ticket Policy**: All s
 ales are final\, no refunds or exchanges.\n\n**SIGNING-UP**\n\n* **RSVP Ye
 s** **\\- everyone goes on the waitlist until they post they purchased the
 ir ticket**\n* **[Purchase](https://www.ripleys.com/attractions/ripleys-aq
 uarium-of-canada?promocode=SS26&utm_source=email&mc_cid=4ca30fd150&mc_eid=
 b8988f8b09)** **your own ticket and select the Sea Star Ball**\, post you 
 have your ticket and I will move you to going.\n\nA reminder will be sent 
 the day before with my cell and reminder details where to meet and when.\n
 \nRSVPs close 2 days prior and the Waitlist will be removed at that time. 
 Cancellations will result in a No Show and impact future attendance.\n\n**
 MEETUP TIME**\n**Meet me at: 8pm inside the entrance of the Ripley's Aquar
 ium at** **288 Bremner Boulevard.**\n\n**We will then head off for some si
 ght seeing prior to joining the lessons\, etc.**\n\nLength: until 12am\n\n
 Enjoy and please post your comments in the Event after.
