SUMMARY:The Great Gatsby Musical - Buy 1 get the 2nd for $1 (Dundas Stn.)
DESCRIPTION:Experience Toronto\n**Note: April Fools Sale Buy 1 get the 2nd
  for $1 expires Apr 2nd at 11:59pm EST.**\n\nOn **Saturday August 15th\, j
 oin us for the Broadway Extravaganza and Tony Award®-winning** **The Grea
 t Gatsby: A New Musical** that explodes with life and energy” (Entertain
 ment Weekly). Based on the classic American novel by F. Scott Fitzgerald\,
  the Tony Award®-winning new musical is an unforgettable journey of love\
 , wealth and tragedy that brings the Roaring Twenties to life on stage. My
  seat is Orchestra N25. **Purchase The Great Gatsby: A New Musical on Satu
 rday August 15th at 7:30pm.**\n\n**COST**\nRegular Cost: $59/ 79/ 109/ 129
 / 159/ 199 + service fees\n\n**Discounted Cost: Buy 1 get the 2nd for $1 a
 pplies to price levels 2- 4** + service fees. The link is embedded in the 
 code. If you can't see it\, use APRILGG\n\nMeetup Organizer Fee: $5\n\n**T
 icket Policy**: All sales are final\, no refunds or exchanges.\n\n**SIGNIN
 G-UP**\n\n* **RSVP Yes confirming if you will join for dinner prior. Note:
  everyone goes on the waitlist until they post their seat number**\n* **[P
 urchase](https://tickets.mirvish.com/gatsby/23779?promoApplied=true)** **y
 our own ticket and select the March 6th date**\, post your seat number and
  I will move you to going.\n\nA reminder will be sent the day before with 
 my cell and reminder details where to meet and when.\n\nRSVPs close 2 days
  prior and the Waitlist will be removed at that time. Cancellations will r
 esult in a No Show and impact future attendance.\n\n**MEETUP TIME**\n**Mee
 t me for Dinner: at 5:45pm (location TBC closer to the event date)**\n\n**
 Meet me for the Show at: 7:15pm inside the CAA Ed Mirvish Theatre at 244 V
 ictoria St. (not the Yonge St. entrance)**\, on the ground floor **to the 
 right side after scanning your tickets.**\n\n**Start: 7:30pm**\n\nLength: 
 2 hours 35 mins (incl. intermission)\n\nAfter: meet at the same spot to ch
 at about the show\n\nEnjoy and please post your comments in the Event afte
 r.
